{hyphenation}
max-consecutive-lines: 3
margin: 2p
space: 3p

{hyphenation: off}
If hyphenation options are set, it hyphenation is also turned on silently.  Then can be toggled on or off.

{hyphenation: on}
If hyphenation options are set, it hyphenation is also turned on silently.  Then can be toggled on or off.
